sql: SELECT Student_Answer_ID FROM Questions_in_Exams JOIN Student_Answers ON Questions_in_Exams.Exam_ID = Student_Answers.Exam_ID AND Student_Answers.Question_ID = Questions_in_Exams.Question_ID WHERE  Student_Answers.Exam_ID >= 78 ORDER BY Student_Answer_ID DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT Question_ID, Valid_Answer_Text FROM Valid_Answers WHERE Question_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  Question_ID != 88 GROUP BY Question_ID HAVING SUM(Valid_Answer_ID) < 93 LIMIT 1
SELECT MAX(o.Exam_ID), o.Exam_Date FROM Exams AS o WHERE  o.Exam_ID = 76 GROUP BY o.Exam_Date HAVING COUNT(o.Exam_ID) >= 48 LIMIT 5

SELECT Student_Answers.Question_ID FROM Questions_in_Exams JOIN Student_Answers ON Questions_in_Exams.Exam_ID = Student_Answers.Exam_ID AND Student_Answers.Question_ID = Questions_in_Exams.Question_ID WHERE  Questions_in_Exams.Question_ID != 42 OR Satisfactory_YN > (SELECT MAX(Satisfactory_YN) FROM Student_Assessments AS w)

SELECT Valid_Answers.Question_ID, Student_Answer_Text, Student_Assessments.Valid_Answer_ID FROM Questions JOIN Valid_Answers JOIN Student_Assessments ON Valid_Answers.Question_ID = Questions.Question_ID AND Valid_Answers.Valid_Answer_ID = Student_Assessments.Valid_Answer_ID WHERE  Valid_Answers.Valid_Answer_ID > 9 GROUP BY Student_Assessments.Valid_Answer_ID HAVING COUNT(Valid_Answers.Valid_Answer_ID) > 69 ORDER BY Student_Assessments.Valid_Answer_ID DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Question_Text), Valid_Answers.Question_ID, Valid_Answer_ID FROM Questions JOIN Valid_Answers ON Valid_Answers.Question_ID = Questions.Question_ID WHERE  Valid_Answer_ID = 20 GROUP BY Valid_Answers.Question_ID
SELECT a.Question_ID FROM Valid_Answers AS a ORDER BY a.Question_ID ASC

SELECT MAX(p.Question_ID), Questions.Question_Text FROM Questions JOIN Questions AS p ON Questions.Question_ID = p.Question_ID WHERE  Questions.Question_ID != 91 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Valid_Answers WHERE Questions.Question_ID = Question_ID) LIMIT 1
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Question_Text), Question_Text, Question_Text, Type_of_Question_Code FROM Questions GROUP BY Type_of_Question_Code HAVING MIN(Question_ID) = 5 LIMIT 3

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Valid_Answer_ID), COUNT(DISTINCT Valid_Answer_ID), Question_ID FROM Valid_Answers WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Questions AS v WHERE  v.Question_ID <= 26 AND Valid_Answers.Valid_Answer_ID = v.Question_ID LIMIT 7)

SELECT d.Subject_Code, d.Subject_Code, d.Exam_Name FROM Exams AS d WHERE Exam_Name IN (SELECT Exam_Name FROM Exams WHERE Exam_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  Exam_ID > 62 LIMIT 9) GROUP BY d.Exam_Name HAVING MAX(d.Exam_ID) < 26 ORDER BY d.Subject_Code ASC

SELECT Question_Text, Type_of_Question_Code FROM Questions JOIN Questions_in_Exams ON Questions.Question_ID = Questions_in_Exams.Question_ID WHERE  Questions.Question_ID <= 40 GROUP BY Type_of_Question_Code HAVING MIN(Questions.Question_ID) >= 59
SELECT Exams.Exam_Name, Exams.Subject_Code, k.Subject_Code FROM Exams JOIN Exams AS k ON Exams.Exam_ID = k.Exam_ID GROUP BY k.Subject_Code ORDER BY Exams.Subject_Code ASC
SELECT Student_Answer_Text, Student_Answer_Text, Comments FROM Student_Answers

SELECT Questions_in_Exams.Exam_ID, Student_Answer_Text FROM Questions_in_Exams JOIN Student_Answers ON Questions_in_Exams.Exam_ID = Student_Answers.Exam_ID AND Student_Answers.Question_ID = Questions_in_Exams.Question_ID WHERE  Questions_in_Exams.Exam_ID <= 59 LIMIT 2
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT u.Cell_Mobile_Phone), u.Last_Name FROM Students AS u WHERE u.Student_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 10

SELECT Questions.Question_ID FROM Questions JOIN Questions_in_Exams JOIN Valid_Answers JOIN Student_Assessments ON Questions.Question_ID = Questions_in_Exams.Question_ID AND Valid_Answers.Question_ID = Questions.Question_ID AND Valid_Answers.Valid_Answer_ID = Student_Assessments.Valid_Answer_ID WHERE  Valid_Answers.Question_ID < 4 ORDER BY Questions.Question_ID DESC

SELECT COUNT(Questions_in_Exams.Exam_ID), Comments FROM Questions JOIN Questions_in_Exams JOIN Student_Answers ON Questions_in_Exams.Exam_ID = Student_Answers.Exam_ID AND Student_Answers.Question_ID = Questions_in_Exams.Question_ID AND Questions.Question_ID = Questions_in_Exams.Question_ID WHERE Student_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Date_of_Answer >= (SELECT MAX(Date_of_Answer) FROM Student_Answers AS p WHERE  p.Question_ID < 71)
SELECT MIN(Student_ID), MAX(Student_ID), MIN(Student_ID) FROM Students WHERE  Student_ID = 52
SELECT Valid_Answer_ID, Question_ID FROM Valid_Answers WHERE  Question_ID != 64 GROUP BY Question_ID HAVING AVG(Valid_Answer_ID) >= 52
SELECT Exams.Subject_Code FROM Exams AS h JOIN Exams ON Exams.Exam_ID = h.Exam_ID

SELECT Type_of_Question_Code, Question_Text FROM Questions JOIN Valid_Answers ON Valid_Answers.Question_ID = Questions.Question_ID WHERE Valid_Answer_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY Question_Text ORDER BY Type_of_Question_Code DESC

SELECT Valid_Answers.Question_ID FROM Questions JOIN Questions_in_Exams JOIN Valid_Answers JOIN Student_Answers ON Questions_in_Exams.Exam_ID = Student_Answers.Exam_ID AND Student_Answers.Question_ID = Questions_in_Exams.Question_ID AND Questions.Question_ID = Questions_in_Exams.Question_ID AND Valid_Answers.Question_ID = Questions.Question_ID WHERE  Student_Answers.Question_ID > 82 ORDER BY Valid_Answers.Question_ID ASC
SELECT u.Subject_Code, u.Exam_Name FROM Exams AS u WHERE u.Exam_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  u.Exam_ID < 48 GROUP BY u.Exam_Name ORDER BY u.Subject_Code ASC

SELECT SUM(i.Valid_Answer_ID), COUNT(DISTINCT i.Valid_Answer_Text), i.Valid_Answer_Text FROM Valid_Answers AS i WHERE  i.Question_ID = 29 OR Question_ID IN (SELECT Question_ID FROM Questions WHERE Question_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 5)

SELECT MIN(Question_ID), Question_Text FROM Questions WHERE  Question_ID = 89 OR Type_of_Question_Code IN (SELECT Type_of_Question_Code FROM Questions AS u WHERE u.Question_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 6)
